            <scopecontent id="aspace_461227c1b011545643ada5ccd7d0d64f">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series contains original and copies of letters from H.D. to Silvia Dobson. Also included in the correspondence are letters to H.D. from Norah, Mollie, and Mervyn Dobson, and Frances Gregg; letters from Kenneth Macpherson to Dobson; and notes by Silvia H. Dobson. The material was compiled by Dobson and entitled "Mirror for a Star, Star for a Mirror: H.D.'s Letters toSilvia Dobson."</p>
            </scopecontent>
